OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally a cloudier day on Saturday,
OL,7,Fbut mostly dry with some bright
OL,8,Fspells. Sunshine returning more widely
OL,9,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fgenerally remaining above average, so
OL,11,Ffeeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
